    public class ConfigDataSourceHandler
extends Object
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.SmartInitializingSingleton

    Config datasource handler dynamically registers the spring Bean according to the configured datasource ConfigRuleProperties,

    In addition, you can extend the ConfigRuleLoadListener listener to implement a custom extension after the ConfigRuleProperties configuration is loaded. And also extend the RuleTypeCustomizer interface to implement personalized extensions for different types of rules
